  note     = {Review paper synthesising clinical and experimental evidence for ADP/ATP carrier autoantibodies in myocarditis and DCM. Establishes that autoimmunity to the ANT may contribute to DCM as a downstream stage of myocarditis. Proposes antibody-mediated reduction of cardiac function via energy imbalance. No abstract available in PubMed; content reconstructed from citing literature. Limitations: review without new primary data; sample details unavailable from abstract.},
